OL,7,FThe chancellor alleged today that
OL,8,FLabour's policy to insulate all
OL,9,FBritish homes would cost more than
OL,10,Fdouble what it has budgeted for. ITV
OL,11,FNews Political Editor Robert Peston
OL,12,Fchallenged those calculations in an
OL,13,Finterview with Jeremy Hunt
OL,15,FThe chancellor has conceded that the
OL,16,FTreasury's #12-15 billion calculation
OL,17,Ffor Labour's plan to improve energy
OL,18,Fefficiency across millions of homes
OL,19,Fmay not be correct.
