OL,3,CHunt admits Treasury's costing of
OL,4,CLabour energy efficiency plans may be
OL,5,Cwrong
OL,7,FLabour previously said the package of
OL,8,Fmeasures would cost a maximum of #6
OL,9,Fbillion a year while bringing down the
OL,10,Fcost of bills for households across
OL,11,Fthe country, subject to Labour's
OL,12,Ffiscal rules.
OL,14,FThe Treasury on Wednesday published a
OL,15,Ffive-page costing of Labour's plan -
OL,16,Fperhaps the first proper tax-and-spend
OL,17,Fsalvo in a general election campaign
OL,18,Fthat could continue for 10 months.
