OL,3,CHunt admits Treasury's costing of
OL,4,CLabour energy efficiency plans may be
OL,5,Cwrong
OL,7,FIt alleged that the opposition's
OL,8,Fpolicy to insulate all British homes
OL,9,Fwould cost more than double what
OL,10,FLabour has budgeted for.
OL,12,FLabour immediately dismissed the
OL,13,Fgovernment's calculations as
OL,14,F"ludicrous" and "bogus".
OL,16,FIn an interview with ITV News
OL,17,FPolitical Editor Robert Peston, Mr
OL,18,FHunt appeared to acknowledge the cost
OL,19,Fmay not be as high as estimated by
OL,20,Fofficials, even as he defended the
OL,21,Fcosting.
