OL,4,CLabour energy efficiency plans may be
OL,5,Cwrong
OL,7,F"We're saying this is not the time to
OL,8,Fgo back to square one," he said. "This
OL,9,Fis a huge sum of money.
OL,11,F"We follow what Labour say themselves
OL,12,Fthey would do. But the point is, it's
OL,13,Fgoing to be expensive."
OL,15,FLabour has rejected the assumption
OL,16,Fthat "all installations are Exchequer-
OL,17,Ffunded", with the party stressing the
OL,18,Fplan would involve a mixture of grants
OL,19,Ffor low-income households and low-
OL,20,Finterest loans for others.
