OL,7,FA party spokesperson said: "This
OL,8,Fcosting is ludicrous and uses bogus
OL,9,Fassumptions. They have costed someone
OL,10,Felse's policy, not Labour's."
OL,12,FIt also noted that the description of
OL,13,Fit as an "uncapped, fully Exchequer-
OL,14,Ffunded, undifferentiated model" does
OL,15,Fnot fit with the party's policy.
OL,17,FThe document was nonetheless seized on
OL,18,Fby the Tories, with Rishi Sunak
OL,19,Fattacking Labour leader Sir Keir
OL,20,FStarmer over the policy at Prime
OL,21,FMinister's Questions.
