OL,7,FThe chancellor was also asked whether
OL,8,Fthe prime minister was wrong to engage
OL,9,Fin gender politics at prime minister's
OL,10,Fquestions when the mother of the
OL,11,Fmurdered trans schoolgirl, Brianna
OL,12,FGhey, was in the Commons.
OL,14,FMr Hunt defended by saying Mr Sunak
OL,15,F"was talking about the fact that Keir
OL,16,FStarmer has changed his position on
OL,17,Fthat as on many other issues" but that
OL,18,F"everyone has been incredibly struck
OL,19,Fby the courage and resolve of
OL,20,FBrianna's mother".
